---
import Page from '../layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Page>
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Services</h1>

    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-10">
      I help small businesses eliminate inefficiencies and unlock revenue through smart CRM automation and integration.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-10 text-lg text-gray-700">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">CRM Workflow Audit</h2>
        <p>
          We identify leaks in your current lead handling, follow-up gaps, and missed automation opportunities.
          This gives us the blueprint to build smarter.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">CRM + Automation Setup</h2>
        <p>
          I work inside your current CRM — whether it's HubSpot, Zoho, Perq, or others — and build customized automations
          that align with your sales process.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Integrations</h2>
        <p>
          We connect your CRM to the tools you already use: Google Sheets, email/SMS platforms, Zapier, and more.
          Everything flows together.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Ongoing Support</h2>
        <p>
          Once the system is running, I provide ongoing tweaks, cleanups, and optimizations to make sure your
          tech keeps up with your business.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10">
      <a href="/" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-5 py-2 rounded hover:bg-blue-700 transition">
        ← Back to Home
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Page>
